com.cloudpos

Interface TimeConstants

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    MSRDevice, PrinterDevice, RFCardReaderDevice, SmartCardReaderDevice

    public interface TimeConstants
    This interface contains a number of useful constants for use with methods that accept a timeout as a parameter.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int FOREVER
      infinite timeout
      static int IMMEDIATE
      zero timeout
      static int MilliSECOND
      milliseconds, for use with millisecond parameters, as in wait( 3 * MSEC )
      static int SECOND
      seconds, for use with millisecond parameters, as in wait( 3 * SEC )
